title: Podcast Episode 133.1 – WITHOUT END by Jenna Hartley
description:
Our audiobook this week is Without End by Jenna Hartley

Turquoise waters.
Endless sand.
Just married.
As an event planner, I’m not used to relinquishing control.
But my new husband makes me want to try.
And I’m coming to realize that when I give in to Harrison, paradise isn’t far behind.
